txt.en: Brigands are stockpiling crossbow bolts in the Bolt-holes.\n\nCollect quivers of crossbow bolts.
The brigands of the Bolt-holes have been stashing armaments.
Brigands are stockpiling crossbow bolts in the Bolt-holes.
As you survey the Bolt-holes, you find many spare quivers of crossbow bolts. Disarming the brigands would help safeguard the passage between Dor-En-Ernil and Ringl√≥ Vale.
You have collected many quivers of crossbow bolts, and should deliver them to someone in Ethring.\n\nDeliver the crossbow bolts to someone in Ethring.

Laerind laughs when you present your bounty of crossbow bolts.

'Hello again, old friend. Now where did you get these?'

You tell her of your encounter at the Bolt-holes. She laughs harder.

'I am glad to see you have not changed since you left Ethring. Always solving problems and helping the common folk, hmm?

'Please make time to speak to Arvaethor while you are here. I am sure he will be as pleased to see you as I am.'
